inputs.text: diqvlvt style manga art, A rosy-pink haired young woman with shoulder-length wavy locks and gold cross earrings stretches both arms overhead, arching her back and lifting her hair as a fitted white athletic tee clings with soft fabric creases and shows two bold chest emblems that read A Dark Infinity LoRA; she wears loose white runner shorts with side slits, drawstring bow, and fine stitching, revealing a toned midriff with a shallow navel and a gentle S-curve hip pop; her expression is serene and focused, eyes half-lidded to the left, lips parted slightly as if exhaling after a deep breath; light perspiration beads on collarbones and upper arms; captured as a full-body, three-quarter view at eye level, centered in frame; bright morning sun pours through tall paned windows behind her, rim-lighting hair strands and casting soft specular highlights and long diagonal shadows on a white windowsill; blurred potted foliage sits to the right, and outside the glass faint church spires and treetops glow in misty distance; dust motes drift through the air; crisp, clean whites and warm peach skin tones dominate; ultra-detailed fabric folds, subtle bokeh, high-resolution clarity.
